Class CSleeping

  • java.lang.Object
    • btrplace.solver.choco.constraint.CSleeping
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ChocoConstraint, MisplacedVMsEstimator

    public class CSleeping
extends Object
implements ChocoConstraint
    Naive implementation of Sleeping. This constraint is just a stub to be consistent with the model. It does not state any constraint as the state has already been expressed inside ReconfigurationProblem.
    Author:
    Fabien Hermenier
